 With fondest memories of our dear Father, Sister & Mother

BILL GILES
1906-1986
Amongst so much else, Dad was once a Scout Leader here at Holy
Trinity Church, a school-teacher & a driving instuctor. Born with
a wanderlust, he came home to his roots to relish his closing years.

MAUREEN GANT
1938-2002
A gifted musician & home-maker, a music teacher & choir-leader,
Maureen lived locally all her life, but was taken from us before her time.

MURIEL GILES
n√©e Selifant
1912 - 2008
Born at Aldon, Ninesprings was both her playground & pathway to school.
After their wanderings, Mum & Dad returned to Yeovil to enjoy retirement until Maureen's early demise took Mum away to her final home in Surrey."„
